Citigroup Hires Emerging-Market Bond Analyst Eric Ollom From Jefferies

-- B y   D r e w   B e n s o n   a n d   V e r o n i c a   N a v a r r o
-- 
2011-05-16T21:43:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/citigroup-hires-emerging-market-bond-analyst-eric-ollom-from-jefferies.html
Citigroup Inc. (C)  hired Eric Ollom as an
emerging-markets debt strategist, luring him away from Jefferies
& Co.  Ollom, 48, will begin working for Citigroup in late June,
bank spokesman Anthony Ingham wrote in an e-mail from  New York .
 Tom Tarrant , a spokesman at Jefferies, declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
